      "writtenOn": "2020-05-04T17:04:33Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "drawPathCoverage is also weird in that it overwrites the entire buffer, so blending doesn\u0027t seem to really be a thing it does. If anything, now the paint has Src set on it (matching the replace op). I believe this is okay; it certainly doesn\u0027t seem to do anything for the A8 images we draw into (or the color images we use as fallback, then read as alpha-only)",
      "parentUuid": "7eef8105_1aed9c58",
      "revId": "6dca0007abdeac7cbdcb016dd7a15ae68193492d",
